title: NFC East Breakdown + Warning Signs, Mustard Man - Fantasy Football Podcast for 7/12
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, a breakdown of the NFC East division! Get an offseason summary and 2022 preview for the Cowboys, Eagles, Giants, and Commanders. Hear differing opinions on Zeke, Saquon Barkley, Terry McLaurin, and others! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for July 12th, 2022
